{{Shield}}
== Overview ==
The Baron II is the strongest deflector of its type. It still wont do much to stop a heavy blast, but it is definitely a step up. Unfortunately the Baron II uses extra power and is quite a bit heavier then the standard Baron.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Baron II Shield can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
